{"tid":28790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我的未來不是夢","createTime":"2016-12-08T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T07:19:42.000Z","uid":4792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"071bda768aa7f7a5bbc1205f4f16501f20ca82e7","tid":28790,"uid":4792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"我的未來不是夢"},{"pid":"df50fd67214a9f7bed961f1c3f88b0a83cdf0b93","tid":28790,"uid":4792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"點解無哂我頭先打既內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我們沒有辦法了解我們自己所虛構的世界的話，根本沒有辦法了解真實的世界。<br />\n所以有一些人說我們的夢想不切實際，但是我覺得，有不切實際的夢想，才是實際的根本。<br />\n<br />\n請你一定要相信自己，一定要接受，喜歡自己的樣子。<br />\n一定要讓自己變成，你真心會喜歡的樣子。<br />\n如果你想做的，不是長輩所控制你的樣子，不是社會所規定你的樣子；<br />\n請你一定要勇敢的為自己站出來，溫柔的推翻這個世界，然後把世界變成我們的﻿。<br />\n<br />\n依幾排好灰，聽完依首歌好有力量，共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzxhaxG5kfY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIzxhaxG5kfY&d=j%2FXJ%2BWVHlSUr%2F5YT%2FLjooEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a69ba7b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzxhaxG5kfY</a>"}]}